    public class MyRebalanceListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.kafka.clients.consumer.ConsumerRebalanceListener
    when a node is added, removed or closed, rebalancing partition assignments take place. this class ensure not processing any duplicated offset. this is a part of the exact-once policy in design.
